            <title><![CDATA[【[二哈]铲屎官注意！#最常见的两种人猫共患病#】猫癣和弓形虫，是两种最常见的人猫共患病。猫癣常见于小猫，患病猫会脱毛、皮屑特别多。人感染猫癣，皮肤会出现...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>铲屎官注意！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9C%80%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%8C%AB%E5%85%B1%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%80%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%8C%AB%E5%85%B1%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#最常见的两种人猫共患病#</span></a>】猫癣和弓形虫，是两种最常见的人猫共患病。猫癣常见于小猫，患病猫会脱毛、皮屑特别多。人感染猫癣，皮肤会出现钱币大小的皮癣；而人接触患有弓形虫病的猫的粪便后，也可能患上弓形虫病，会导致孕妇的流产和畸胎。不过，家猫不外出不吃生肉，基本不可能感染弓形虫病👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%96%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E7%94%9F%E8%82%89%E7%9A%84%E7%8C%AB%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%E5%BC%93%E5%BD%A2%E8%99%AB%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%96%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E7%94%9F%E8%82%89%E7%9A%84%E7%8C%AB%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%E5%BC%93%E5%BD%A2%E8%99%AB%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不外出不吃生肉的猫不用担心弓形虫病#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6CpN0x0" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
